The internal Tweedieverse implementation in this package is adapted from the
Tweedieverse package by Himel Mallick and Ali Rahnavard.

Only the modeling code needed by DAssemble's Tweedieverse core method is bundled
here; visualization and standalone package interfaces are not exported.

The internal Robseq implementation is adapted from the Robseq package developed
by the lab. Only the modeling code needed by DAssemble's Robseq core method is
bundled here; the standalone package interface is not exported.
